Dialogs.Dialog: I heard there's someone in the tennis club that you've been hanging out with lately.
I heard that you've been getting along with someone at your part-time job lately.
I see, then it was true. You're surprisingly good at it.
Oh well. That's youth for you. Huhu！
How it that girl from the tennis club these days？
How is that girl at your part-time job doing these days？
Progress, huh. It's not like that...
There you go again. Don't you like any of them？
(That's it for today's committee activities... Huh, where are you ▲小早川＊▲？)
"I'll be waiting for you on the rooftop. -Rinko."
What's wrong, why did you call me here...？ Hah.
Why are you so upset, did you think Rinko was crying again？
Hehe... But as you can see, I'm fine.
It's just... I wanted to thank you again.
When Rinko was in trouble, you helped her out.
You helped me when I got in trouble at the arcade, with my family... You helped Rinko when she was alone.
You're really like an older brother.
Yes, you're a little sister ▲小早川＊▲.
Will you continue to be... Rinko's... onii-chan？
Yes, I can't take my eyes off of you.
Thank you so much. Please stay with me from now on.
(That's it for today's committee activities... Huh, where are you ▲小早川＊▲？)
(I was remembering when you confessed to me, ▲小早川＊▲...)
(That's it for today's committee activities... Huh, where are you ▲小早川＊▲？)
"What are you ding？ I'm on the rooftop. -Rinko."
(I was remembering when you confessed to me, ▲小早川＊▲...)
(That's it for today's committee activities... Huh, where are you ▲小早川＊▲？)
(Sunset？ So, you're on the rooftop... No way...)
(I was remembering when you confessed to me, ▲小早川＊▲...)
(That's it for today's committee activities... Huh, where are you ▲小早川＊▲？)
Good grief, you've got a girlfriend. There, the end.
(I feel bad for her... even in a dream...)
Say... don't you think Rinko has changed？
Well, it's not about looks. You know, on the inside.
Inside, hug... Well, you're kind of quiet.
Yes. I'm trying to be a little more relaxed.
Hmm, I just did. I thought it would be nice if I tried it.
(A calmer version of you. That might be nice, ▲小早川＊▲...)
Don't stare at me, I'll kick you.
I'm not trying to scare you... I thought I'd be a bit more aggressive.
Well, I don't want to be kicked...
That was a joke. But, I thought you might not like it.
(A stronger version of you. That might be nice, ▲小早川＊▲...)
Say, don't you think Rinko has changed a bit？
Geez, you don't get it. Rinko is sad.
Yes, that's it. Rinko-chan is honest and cheerful. Not bad, right？
But why all of a sudden？
Somehow I though you'd be happier if I did this.
(A more honest version of you. That might be nice, ▲小早川＊▲...)
Say, do you often go to eat at Winning Burger, ▲小早川＊▲？
Pretty much. I'm a heavy user.
I see, it's typical for high school students.
What's with that answer. Well, yes, there are a lot of high school students.
I don't think anyone from our school hasn't been there.
Hmm, I don't know. Do you know everyone？
Say, do you ofter browse Towano Watcher, right, ▲小早川＊▲？
Well, I do, but why do you want to know？
I was wondering if someone who is not familiar with going out with others, can rely on magazines to invite others.
Nothing beats experience, right？ Maybe if you have someone else with you.
(I knew it... I hope you are doing okay... ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
Say, what do you think about going to practice for chaperoning a date ▲小早川＊▲？
I knew that's how you'd react.
I don't know, but... isn't that a date？
What, did you get invited on a date？ No way.
(I guess that was a date... I guess I shouldn't have said no to you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
Say, what would you do if you were invited out to dinner by a senior at your part-time job, ▲小早川＊▲？
Well, it's going to be a mess.
I guess it depends on the level of seniority of that senior, but... you don't have to think too much about it, do you？
Especially if you don't dislike that senior.
I was asked to come up with an idea for a new menu at my part-time job.
Eh, that sounds like a hassle. Is that a part-time job？
I knew you would say that.
Unless there is some perk to it.
(Perks, huh... I think being able to go out with you is one of those, ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲...)
If I promised to go out with you, I have to fulfill it, right？
Well, of course. We made a promise.
It's irresponsible for a person to break a promise.
(Well, that's right... What should I do about my promise with you, ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲.)
What, you're dazed... Ah no, it's your usual self.
Hey... For real, what's wrong？ You're weird.
I was just remembering you are my girlfriend, ▲小早川＊▲.
...I know. What am I thinking about？
It's not that, I was just remembering things.
We met, and things happened since then――
Did you find something when remembering？
I knew that you were the only one for me, ▲小早川＊▲...
You were telling me about remembering things before we started dating.
